{"tid":1804451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【RTHK】武漢出現不明原因肺炎個案　惹重現沙士憂慮","createTime":"2019-12-31T04:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:52:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45af4244672cda2181435336ea2a2615b8f04b61","tid":1804451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500292-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500292-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=62bd404e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500292-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=61b80a97\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500292-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢部分醫療機構出現不明原因的肺炎個案，當局已經對患者採取隔離措施，並表示將第一時間公布檢測結果。央視報道，國家衛健委專家組上午抵達武漢，展開相關檢測核實工作。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市衛生健康委員會日前發公告，說武漢市華南海鮮市場陸續出現不明原因肺炎，要求各醫療機構及時追蹤統計救治情況，並按要求及時上報。武漢疾控部門正前往救治醫院採集患者樣本。<br />\n<br />\n有報道引述上海市同濟大學的消息說，今次武漢肺炎病原體與俗稱沙士的「非典型肺炎」，同屬冠狀病毒。"},{"pid":"d372058cf96be0fcf046c019098d9dd0ab9043de","tid":1804451,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=1253a457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=49a5f